Recover some stamina and soul power.

44
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,336
Land soul masters defeated

45
00:04:32,352 --> 00:04:34,040
ocean soul masters of the same level.

46
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,392
This is my first time seeing it.

47
00:04:35,568 --> 00:04:37,090
It has broadened my horizons indeed.

48
00:04:37,090 --> 00:04:39,056
We already saw
how the ocean soul masters fought

49
00:04:39,088 --> 00:04:40,210
when we observed the battle.

50
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:42,450
But that was a close shave indeed.

51
00:04:42,496 --> 00:04:43,744
I'm glad that you guys are fine.

52
00:04:43,872 --> 00:04:45,380
Sorry for making you guys worried.

53
00:04:45,410 --> 00:04:46,850
Next time, I'll be more cautious.

54
