296
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:23,620
and change the situation
in Douluo Continent.

297
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:32,570
It has left the sea for too long.

298
00:15:33,296 --> 00:15:35,260
Being able
to go on adventures with you all

299
00:15:35,650 --> 00:15:36,340
might be

300
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:39,380
its best destiny.

301
00:15:40,864 --> 00:15:41,890
Thank you, Elder Ocean.

302
00:16:10,570 --> 00:16:13,690
Welcome to the Sea Devil.

303
00:16:14,380 --> 00:16:15,100
Besides me,

304
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,290
there's one first mate

305
00:16:17,290 --> 00:16:19,340
and four crew members.

306
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:20,896
Captain Hai,

307
00:16:20,912 --> 00:16:22,368
how do you deal with the ferocious

308
00:16:22,384 --> 00:16:23,184
ocean soul beasts

309
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,160
when you encounter them?

310
00:16:25,890 --> 00:16:29,020
Although ocean soul beasts
may seem ferocious and violent,

311
00:16:29,570 --> 00:16:32,650
if you don't provoke them

312
00:16:32,770 --> 00:16:34,380
or attack their territories,

313
00:16:35,140 --> 00:16:36,930
they won't be enraged.

314
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:40,890
If so, they won't attack our ship.

315
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:43,980
However, if you guys provoke them

316
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:46,290
by accident,

317
00:16:46,570 --> 00:16:47,890
and they become enraged,

318
00:16:48,128 --> 00:16:50,432
