yourselves for being unlucky by then.

319
00:16:53,344 --> 00:16:55,100
Mr. Hai, you're a veteran of the sea.

320
00:16:55,170 --> 00:16:56,690
Please lead the way.

321
00:16:57,570 --> 00:16:58,410
Just leave it to me.

322
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:00,980
Remove the anchor!

323
00:17:01,650 --> 00:17:03,410
Set sail!

324
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:06,370
Set sail!

325
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:08,220
