326
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:31,420
Stop acting tough.

327
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,330
Go and throw up.

328
00:17:45,824 --> 00:17:47,664
It's pointing to
the northwest of Hanhai City.

329
00:17:47,980 --> 00:17:50,130
Indeed. We're heading to Haishen Island.

330
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:53,260
Wu?

331
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:55,370
