00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:16,528
I'll lead the soul master army
to attack all of the territories.

388
00:20:16,592 --> 00:20:18,672
We shall plant our flags
all over the continent

389
00:20:18,672 --> 00:20:21,180
and make final preparations
for the establishment of our nation.

390
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:24,700
Remember,

