433
00:22:04,768 --> 00:22:06,050
Since you've improved our meals,

434
00:22:06,050 --> 00:22:07,248
I'll improve our mood, then.

435
00:22:07,296 --> 00:22:08,816
Or it'll be boring
to spend our days

436
00:22:08,832 --> 00:22:09,792
on the sea like this.

437
00:22:10,368 --> 00:22:11,090
Excellent words.

438
00:22:11,330 --> 00:22:13,130
I'll tell you guys a joke, then.

439
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:14,660
Life is unpredictable.

440
00:22:14,810 --> 00:22:15,610
Maybe

441
00:22:16,020 --> 00:22:17,770
this is our last meal.

442
00:22:20,570 --> 00:22:21,420
Capture them alive.

443
00:22:22,090 --> 00:22:24,220
Hand them to Martial Soul Hall.

444
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,660
So, are you from Martial Soul Hall?

445
00:22:40,530 --> 00:22:41,570
Thanks to you guys,

446
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:43,220
I'll be their member soon.

447
00:22:43,370 --> 00:22:45,570
You guys have a deep feud
against Martial Soul Hall.

448
00:22:46,050 --> 00:22:47,610
If I hand you guys to them,

449
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:50,460
I'll definitely have
a bright future ahead of me.

450
00:22:55,370 --> 00:22:57,610
I'm afraid you won't get
what you wished for.

451
00:23:04,352 --> 00:23:05,290
How could this be?

452
00:23:06,130 --> 00:23:07,370
Are you curious

453
00:23:07,740 --> 00:23:09,420
