your men fell unconscious first?

454
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:10,740
I found out

455
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,420
that our meals were spiked by accident.

456
00:23:12,592 --> 00:23:14,130
That's very thoughtful of you guys.

457
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:16,370
You guys should enjoy them yourselves.

458
00:23:22,384 --> 00:23:23,810
Rongrong and the rest are asleep.

459
00:23:23,940 --> 00:23:25,090
I won't wake them up.

460
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:27,180
I've been confirming our direction
using the compass

461
00:23:27,184 --> 00:23:28,590
and the sun
for the past few days.

462
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:30,544
