465
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:38,912
Those crew members were keeping
a close eye on us.

466
00:23:38,976 --> 00:23:40,256
I suppose they were monitoring

467
00:23:40,288 --> 00:23:42,090
our daily routine and behaviors.

468
00:23:42,770 --> 00:23:44,180
I'll interrogate them now.

469
00:23:44,610 --> 00:23:45,260
Fatty,

470
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,880
do not alert them to our presence.

471
00:23:46,912 --> 00:23:48,496
We'll wait for him to give himself away.

472
00:23:48,512 --> 00:23:50,096
I think he can't hold it in any longer.

473
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:50,850
That's right.

474
00:23:51,220 --> 00:23:52,570
We have to be very cautious.

475
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:55,090
Besides, tell Xiang to examine the meals

476
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:56,500
when she scouts the ship.

477
00:24:11,570 --> 00:24:13,180
You guys are pretty witty, huh?

478
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,570
This must be what you do usually.

479
00:24:15,616 --> 00:24:17,850
You'll make up an excuse
to bring people out to the sea.

480
00:24:17,856 --> 00:24:20,112
Then you'll get rid of them
and steal their possessions.

481
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:23,040
