487
00:24:35,090 --> 00:24:36,610
We're on the sea.

488
00:24:37,020 --> 00:24:38,050
Without me,

489
00:24:38,050 --> 00:24:39,824
none of you gets
to leave the place alive!

490
00:24:39,872 --> 00:24:40,912
All of you will die!

491
00:24:40,980 --> 00:24:42,900
Since you wish
to serve Martial Soul Hall,

492
00:24:44,770 --> 00:24:46,130
I cannot keep you alive.

493
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:04,220
No!

494
00:25:21,090 --> 00:25:22,180
Sir, please spare me!

495
00:25:22,330 --> 00:25:23,220
Sir, please spare me!

496
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:23,940
Sir!

497
00:25:24,330 --> 00:25:25,810
I was just muddle-headed!

498
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:28,940
