504
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:40,528
What kind of organization
is the Purple Pearl?

505
00:25:40,530 --> 00:25:41,330
Who's the leader?

506
00:25:43,090 --> 00:25:44,570
The Purple Pearl,

507
00:25:46,290 --> 00:25:47,220
