508
00:25:47,660 --> 00:25:48,570
We can reach

509
00:25:48,850 --> 00:25:50,130
Purple Pearl Island in two days.

510
00:25:50,144 --> 00:25:51,728
They make a living by robbing people.

511
00:25:51,810 --> 00:25:53,700
Their leader, Purple Pearl,

512
00:25:53,810 --> 00:25:54,460
