513
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:56,290
a Level 73 soul saint.

514
00:25:56,900 --> 00:25:58,420
We're merely normal members.

515
00:25:59,050 --> 00:26:01,610
We head to the pier to find victims.

516
00:26:01,850 --> 00:26:03,940
After that, we'll rob them on the sea.

517
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:05,180
