524
00:26:21,530 --> 00:26:22,290
Get up.

525
00:26:34,330 --> 00:26:35,850
Lead us to Haishen Island.

526
00:26:36,090 --> 00:26:37,330
But don't try anything funny.

527
00:26:37,504 --> 00:26:39,260
I've already sealed
your soul power away.

528
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:40,530
If you try something funny,

529
00:26:41,020 --> 00:26:42,370
