531
00:26:45,610 --> 00:26:46,180
Yes, sir!

532
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:47,180
Yes, sir!

533
00:26:52,980 --> 00:26:53,770
San,

534
00:26:53,808 --> 00:26:55,090
are we letting him off already?

535
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:56,290
Fatty,

536
00:26:56,770 --> 00:26:57,940
